      "span_text": "The diminished ability for certain people to vasodilate the peripheral circulation is well documented in the scientific literature.  We should therefore be accounting for this biological factor, and work to protect the various populations who deploy in harsh arctic conditions by providing the best clothing, methods for prevention the best medical treatment available."
